high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the salt shaker to the left of the lettuce.
Turn around and walk to the counter ahead.
Open the drawer to the right, place the salt in the drawer, and close it.
turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove and look at the cabinet above.
Open the left door of the cabinet, take the salt shaker out, and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the drawer the first salt shaker is in.
Open the drawer, put the salt shaker inside the drawer behind the first shaker, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers inside of a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around, walk straight towards the sink and turn right to the stove.
Pick up the salt that is next to the lettuce.
Walk to your right and go to the cabinet with a knife on the counter top.
Put the salt in the drawer underneath the counter top.
Walk to your left until you see a loaf of bread.
Grab another bottle of salt from the cabinet on top of the bread.
Turn around and go back to the counter top with a knife on top of it again.
Open the drawer under the cabinet, put the bottle of salt next to the other salt and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put 2 bottles of salt in the drawer of the cabinet that has a knife on the counter top.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the stove.
Pick up the saltshaker to the left of the romaine lettuce.
Turn right and take a step to your right then walk to the counter in front of you.
Open the top drawer that's under the counter top and put the saltshaker in it in the bottom left corner before closing it.
Turn left and walk to the counter, you should be facing the bread.
Open the left cabinet door above the bread on the counter and get the salt shaker before closing the door.
Walk back to where you put the first salt shaker.
Put the salt shaker above the other one in the bottom left corner.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn around to go to the counter left of the stove
Pick up the salt shaker.
Go to the counter with drawers on the right.
Place the salt shaker in the top drawer on the right side of the counter next to the spoon.
Turn left and go to the counter on the right of the stove.
Open the cupboard above the counter and remove the salt shaker.
Turn around to go back to the counter with the drawer with salt shaker in it.
Place the salt shaker behind the first salt shaker in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place salt shakers in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn around, go straight to the coffee maker, turn right go to the counter to the left of the oven.
Take the salt on the left of the counter.
Turn around, go straight, turn left where the counter ends on the left, go straight to the counter.
Put the salt in the left side bottom corner of the drawer below the counter.
Turn left, go straight to the counter.
Take the salt from the cabinet above the oven and counter.
Turn around, go back to the end of the counter and face the counter.
Put the salt above the other salt in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two salts in a drawer.
